  <brief_title>Immobilization in External Rotation After First Time Anterior Shoulder Dislocation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Immobilization in External Rotation After First Time Anterior Shoulder Dislocation: A Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
