  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of immobilization in internal versus external rotation after first time anterior
      shoulder dislocation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare immobilization in internal versus external rotation
      after first time anterior shoulder dislocation, and thereby increase our knowledge about the
      best standard of care.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
